title: Added a delay checkbox
message:
Added a delay checkbox

If Tie to SMS is enabled as well as Delay dismissal, we wait 5 seconds before
dismissing our notification. This is to cope for sms apps like Samsung's,
which always deletes its active notification (if any) then recreates it upon a
new message.

title: Implemented a ContentObserver for the SMS database
message:
Implemented a ContentObserver for the SMS database

Not guaranteed to work on all devices (esp JellyBean and older), and on KitKat
+, different apps notify a db change differently (eg, Hangouts does not update
the "seen" column whereas Messaging does not update the "read" column.

title: Changed to LOOKUP_KEY for Contact calls
message:
Changed to LOOKUP_KEY for Contact calls

compared to the Fragment contact list. LOOKUP_KEY seems to be common for both
of them.
